<plot>The host for Epic America travels the country scouting and finding extreme sports that have become quite popular. From skateboarding, to wakeboarding, to tree climbing, out host will dive into each sport and reveal the athletes, the rules, and the respect each sport is trying or has received. Within each location, we will also explore the demographic, the "night life", and the culture. It will show what there is to do in some of America's (and the World's) hottest locations.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?164076</url></doc>
